node.text:
It’s an honor to have my special “Asian Momma, Mexican Kids” included in @netflix, Best of Stand-Up 2020!
This is an end-of-year special where you'll get a chance to rewatch some of your favorite comedians of the year or discover new ones you may have missed.
 
Join us as we take a look back at some of the jokes that got us through the year in this compilation of stand-up highlights.
 
The Best of 2020 Stand-Ups is streaming globally NOW on @netflixisajoke!!
